539
00:23:53,800 --> 00:23:54,919
What do you think?

540
00:23:55,080 --> 00:23:56,719
Do you want me...

541
00:23:56,719 --> 00:23:58,280
to lie to them for you?

542
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:01,919
Please, Dr. Tang.

543
00:24:02,320 --> 00:24:03,919
I really don't want to have children.

544
00:24:04,280 --> 00:24:05,560
You don't want to have children?

545
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:07,679
