546
00:24:08,320 --> 00:24:09,639
How?

547
00:24:11,760 --> 00:24:13,919
My father-in-law wants a grandchild.

548
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:16,560
Although my husband doesn't say it,

549
00:24:17,399 --> 00:24:18,439
I know...

550
00:24:18,439 --> 00:24:20,240
that he wants to have our baby.

551
00:24:21,800 --> 00:24:22,919
Dr. Tang.

552
00:24:24,359 --> 00:24:26,639
My husband is really good to me.

553
00:24:26,719 --> 00:24:28,560
I don't know how to tell him.

554
00:24:31,280 --> 00:24:33,040
You don't want to disappoint your family...

555
00:24:33,320 --> 00:24:35,119
but you don't want to have a baby.

556
00:24:35,800 --> 00:24:38,560
So you want to use this accident as an excuse?

557
00:24:39,560 --> 00:24:40,639
Yes.

558
00:24:40,840 --> 00:24:43,159
I really don't know what else to do, Dr. Tang.

559
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:45,000
I'll be honest with you.

560
00:24:45,600 --> 00:24:47,080
When I think about having children,

561
00:24:47,159 --> 00:24:48,240
I'm so scared.

562
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:49,719
I'm scared...

563
00:24:49,919 --> 00:24:51,000
I'm so scared that I'm shaking all over.

564
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:52,480
Why?

565
00:24:57,919 --> 00:24:59,000
It's okay.

566
00:24:59,399 --> 00:25:00,800
You don't have to tell me.

567
00:25:01,080 --> 00:25:02,280
Dr. Tang.

568
00:25:02,560 --> 00:25:03,639
I'll tell you.

569
00:25:04,119 --> 00:25:06,119
But you have to keep it a secret.

570
00:25:24,520 --> 00:25:26,719
Although I don't have your background or experience,

571
00:25:26,959 --> 00:25:28,359
I deeply understand...

572
00:25:28,359 --> 00:25:29,800
why you're afraid to have children.

573
00:25:30,280 --> 00:25:31,919
Thank you, Dr. Tang.

574
00:25:32,359 --> 00:25:34,040
But as a doctor,

575
00:25:34,639 --> 00:25:35,800
I can't help you.

576
00:25:36,199 --> 00:25:38,560
We doctors have our own protocol.

577
00:25:38,840 --> 00:25:40,119
Don't you understand...

578
00:25:40,679 --> 00:25:42,600
what I've been through?

579
00:25:42,879 --> 00:25:43,879
Yes.

580
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:45,280
I do.

581
00:25:46,199 --> 00:25:49,199
But first, you have to tell them your difficulties.

582
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:50,840
You have to communicate with them.

583
00:25:50,959 --> 00:25:52,359
I think they will understand.

584
00:25:57,240 --> 00:25:58,320
Dr. Tang.

585
00:25:58,800 --> 00:26:00,000
You're not married, are you?

586
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:02,719
Does it matter?

587
00:26:03,040 --> 00:26:05,159
You won't understand since you're not married.

588
00:26:08,520 --> 00:26:09,760
All right, Dr. Tang.

589
00:26:11,399 --> 00:26:12,600
I won't put you on the spot.

590
00:26:15,919 --> 00:26:17,480
Pretend I didn't say anything.

591
00:26:23,600 --> 00:26:26,080
People these days need to learn to communicate better.

592
00:26:26,119 --> 00:26:28,199
Are you going to talk about a patient's personal matter again?

593
00:26:28,199 --> 00:26:29,520
I just feel emotional.

594
00:26:29,639 --> 00:26:30,760
From them,

595
00:26:30,760 --> 00:26:33,040
I've learned a lot about communication.

596
00:26:33,399 --> 00:26:34,840
It can be regarded as a preventive measure.

597
00:26:35,080 --> 00:26:36,800
Stop talking about patients' family matters.

598
00:26:36,840 --> 00:26:38,520
Don't let Mom Lu hear you or you'll get scolded.

599
00:26:38,879 --> 00:26:39,919
It's almost midnight.

600
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:41,359
Go home and get some rest.

601
00:26:41,359 --> 00:26:43,000
I'm so angry that my blood pressure is rising.

602
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:44,119
I can't sleep at all.

603
00:26:44,719 --> 00:26:46,639
It's not safe lately. Do you need a ride?

604
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:47,840
With you?

605
00:26:48,199 --> 00:26:49,679
It's safer to go back on my own.

606
00:26:50,719 --> 00:26:52,639
Aren't you afraid of being robbed or molested?

607
00:26:52,639 --> 00:26:54,600
Isn't that person already under watch?

608
00:26:55,639 --> 00:26:56,639
You're right.

609
00:26:56,719 --> 00:26:58,719
Him getting out of the EICU to molest you...

610
00:26:58,840 --> 00:27:00,159
is a bit too much.

611
00:27:00,719 --> 00:27:01,719
Annoying.

612
00:27:08,840 --> 00:27:11,199
(Chen Zhi)

613
00:27:13,359 --> 00:27:15,520
Did something happen at the hospital?

614
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:16,800
No.

615
00:27:16,919 --> 00:27:19,040
I just wanted to ask where you are.

616
00:27:19,320 --> 00:27:20,439
I'm on my way home.

617
00:27:21,919 --> 00:27:23,119
Are you taking a taxi?

618
00:27:23,399 --> 00:27:25,159
Yes. What's the matter?

619
00:27:25,639 --> 00:27:27,040
Are you alone?

620
00:27:27,359 --> 00:27:29,000
Who else could there be?

621
00:27:29,480 --> 00:27:31,879
Take a look at the driver.

622
00:27:31,959 --> 00:27:33,080
Does he look like a bad guy?

623
00:27:36,719 --> 00:27:37,760
Are you crazy?

624
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:38,959
If there's nothing else, I'm hanging up.

625
00:27:55,919 --> 00:27:56,959
What now?

626
00:27:57,719 --> 00:27:59,959
I want to ask where you are.

627
00:28:00,080 --> 00:28:02,480
I just hung up on you one minute ago.

628
00:28:02,800 --> 00:28:04,280
I'm still on my way home.

629
00:28:04,919 --> 00:28:06,600
Then take a good look.

630
00:28:06,719 --> 00:28:08,520
Is the driver a bad person?

631
00:28:08,800 --> 00:28:10,320
If there's nothing, I'm hanging up.

632
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:19,480
(Chen Zhi)

633
00:28:28,399 --> 00:28:29,840
Aren't you on night duty?

634
00:28:30,199 --> 00:28:31,240
Dr. Xu.

635
00:28:31,719 --> 00:28:33,040
I've been calling Tang Hua...

636
00:28:33,119 --> 00:28:34,240
but she isn't picking up.

637
00:28:34,280 --> 00:28:35,359
Could something have happened to her?

638
00:28:35,359 --> 00:28:36,679
What's wrong with you? Are you sick?

639
00:28:36,879 --> 00:28:38,080
Get back to your night shift.

640
00:28:40,080 --> 00:28:41,439
Cranial CT scan suggests...

641
00:28:41,439 --> 00:28:43,119
