642
00:28:43,399 --> 00:28:44,760
But no bloody cerebrospinal fluid...

643
00:28:44,760 --> 00:28:45,760
was found in the lumbar puncture.

644
00:28:46,119 --> 00:28:47,879
Is it intracranial venous sinus thrombosis?

645
00:28:48,199 --> 00:28:50,119
But the cerebrospinal fluid cell count,

646
00:28:50,159 --> 00:28:52,480
biochemical proteins, chloride and sugar...

647
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,840
are all within the normal range.

648
00:28:58,679 --> 00:28:59,719
Hello.

649
00:28:59,719 --> 00:29:01,439
Dr. Bai, the patient in bed five is awake.

650
00:29:02,119 --> 00:29:03,199
You had a ruptured spleen.

651
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:04,879
We've done surgery for you.

652
00:29:05,119 --> 00:29:06,840
After a blood transfusion...

653
00:29:06,840 --> 00:29:07,840
Doctor.

654
00:29:08,399 --> 00:29:09,560
How long was I unconscious?

655
00:29:10,919 --> 00:29:12,480
How is Ding Xiao Ying?

656
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:13,600
Who?

657
00:29:13,600 --> 00:29:15,320
The girl who was brought here with him.

658
00:29:15,679 --> 00:29:16,879
Her life isn't in danger.

659
00:29:16,919 --> 00:29:19,040
But her cornea was ruptured in both eyes.

660
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:21,119
Sutures didn't work and she lost her sight.

661
00:29:21,159 --> 00:29:22,280
How did that happen?

662
00:29:22,879 --> 00:29:24,399
Can she be cured?

663
00:29:24,719 --> 00:29:26,800
You should worry more about yourself.

664
00:29:26,919 --> 00:29:28,159
Pervert.

665
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:31,320
She...

666
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:33,280
Can she be cured or not?

667
00:29:33,560 --> 00:29:35,199
As long as we find a suitable cornea,

668
00:29:35,399 --> 00:29:36,480
there's still hope for recovery.

669
00:29:36,959 --> 00:29:37,959
Can I see her?

670
00:29:38,080 --> 00:29:39,159
No.

671
00:29:45,800 --> 00:29:47,040
Will you have any trouble finding the cornea?

672
00:29:48,040 --> 00:29:49,119
Dr. Bai.

673
00:29:50,719 --> 00:29:51,800
How is he?

674
00:29:52,040 --> 00:29:53,679
He just woke up. He's still a bit weak.

675
00:29:54,320 --> 00:29:55,439
Are you Luo Guang Liang?

676
00:29:56,560 --> 00:29:57,600
Yes.

677
00:29:57,800 --> 00:29:58,840
You are...

678
00:29:58,959 --> 00:30:00,560
We're from Tuanjie Road Police Station.

679
00:30:00,760 --> 00:30:01,840
We suspect...

680
00:30:01,840 --> 00:30:04,439
that you're connected to several recent attacks on women.

681
00:30:04,719 --> 00:30:05,919
Please cooperate.

682
00:30:06,159 --> 00:30:08,040
Attacks on women?

683
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:10,359
There's been a misunderstanding.

684
00:30:10,919 --> 00:30:12,320
Do you know her?

685
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:15,080
Yes.

686
00:30:17,000 --> 00:30:18,399
At 11:30pm on the night of the accident...

687
00:30:18,399 --> 00:30:19,800
at Tuanjie West Road,

688
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:21,439
why were you following her?

689
00:30:21,719 --> 00:30:23,080
I wasn't following her.

690
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:25,080
I was trying to protect her.

691
00:30:28,199 --> 00:30:29,520
I'm a cashier...

692
00:30:29,760 --> 00:30:31,119
at a convenience store on Tuanjie Road.

693
00:30:32,320 --> 00:30:33,639
Not far from my store...

694
00:30:33,800 --> 00:30:34,840
is a café.

695
00:30:35,119 --> 00:30:36,959
She's a server there.

696
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,760
Her café doesn't provide food,

697
00:30:40,159 --> 00:30:42,399
so she often buys lunch at the convenience store.

698
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:44,280
She's very gentle when she talks.

699
00:30:45,119 --> 00:30:47,040
But she doesn't seem to have many friends.

700
00:30:47,840 --> 00:30:49,080
She's always alone.

701
00:30:49,719 --> 00:30:51,639
After she finishes her lunch at the store,

702
00:30:51,639 --> 00:30:52,719
she goes back.

703
00:30:54,159 --> 00:30:55,439
Many people leave a lot of trash behind...

704
00:30:55,879 --> 00:30:57,480
after they finish their food.

705
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,119
But not her.

706
00:30:59,399 --> 00:31:01,959
She would clean up after her.

707
00:31:02,639 --> 00:31:04,679
She'd even wipe the table with the wet wipes...

708
00:31:04,879 --> 00:31:06,159
that she brought along.

709
00:31:08,679 --> 00:31:09,919
She...

710
00:31:10,399 --> 00:31:12,359
is a kind and thoughtful girl.

711
00:31:12,639 --> 00:31:14,959
Is that when you noticed her?

712
00:31:15,359 --> 00:31:17,320
Do you like her?

713
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:22,919
I've never dated anyone before.

714
00:31:24,080 --> 00:31:26,959
I guess I like her.

715
00:31:28,040 --> 00:31:30,080
Because I'm always involuntarily...

716
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:31,480
thinking about her...

717
00:31:32,199 --> 00:31:33,399
and want to see her.

718
00:31:34,439 --> 00:31:36,399
