719
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:39,080
I would feel terrible on that day.

720
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,240
Later,

721
00:31:42,280 --> 00:31:44,119
I noticed that in her eyes...

722
00:31:44,879 --> 00:31:46,679
is a faint sadness.

723
00:31:47,119 --> 00:31:48,600
It's heartbreaking.

724
00:31:49,320 --> 00:31:51,080
Ding Xiao Ying is an orphan.

725
00:31:53,280 --> 00:31:54,359
I only found out...

726
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:55,959
after I overheard...

727
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:57,359
her colleagues talking.

728
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:59,399
Since then,

729
00:31:59,439 --> 00:32:00,679
when I knew she was coming,

730
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:02,840
I'd always hide the best lunch box...

731
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:04,159
and save it for her.

732
00:32:04,760 --> 00:32:07,879
But she never noticed.

733
00:32:08,119 --> 00:32:09,800
You can be more proactive.

734
00:32:10,359 --> 00:32:11,879
She doesn't want to be bothered.

735
00:32:13,080 --> 00:32:14,879
I've seen someone confess their love to her before.

736
00:32:15,320 --> 00:32:16,639
It was her colleague.

737
00:32:17,719 --> 00:32:19,879
He seemed like a nice guy...

738
00:32:19,879 --> 00:32:21,119
but she rejected him.

739
00:32:22,800 --> 00:32:23,840
I know...

740
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:26,560
that she doesn't want to interact with anyone at all.

741
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:28,959
She just wants to live in peace.

